episodes.title: Virginia Giuffre's ghostwriter: What Prince Andrew does next
episodes.description:
“If you care so deeply about this, he could share that information with investigators.” 

Virginia Giuffre’s ghostwriter Amy Wallace says Prince Andrew could right his wrongs by working with investigators to bring Epstein’s victims justice.
